{"tid":255481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台長fb嘆：又嚟返工返學先嚟落大雨！","createTime":"2017-05-24T02:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T01:32:12.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"767f779340758028fef1b791a1a53d057cef486f","tid":255481,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170524/photo/bkn-20170524085741507-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170524094204\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170524085741507-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170524094204&h=cf179329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早返工返學時間下大雨，天文台發出上午6時40分發出黃色暴雨警告，其後於9時15分改發紅色暴雨警告，天文台台長岑智明今早亦在其社交網站facebook發貼留言：「又黎(嚟)返工返學時間先至黎(嚟)落大雨」！<br />\n<br />\n今早在天文台發出黃雨警告尚未發紅雨警告之際，有網民回應台長留言稱，今早返工全身濕透了，另有人又留言問台長：「返工返學時間，達標都唔出紅雨？」有網民隨即代台長回覆稱，「唔夠廣泛」。"},{"pid":"8d5795e415fdd31bdac9c8020de492303669c5f8","tid":255481,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d308903430e0be418ccede6743e739f1ef0565c6","tid":255481,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:03:25.000Z","msg":"食屎啦,仆街"},{"pid":"fbb5f27734ba22b7c1cba3a822d70aeecab3a6b0","tid":255481,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"成個周融咁撚樣"},{"pid":"bdd2f6b275e495f093dc0e569a4b873a03c1d66e","tid":255481,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"死全家"},{"pid":"0ab55f5ab89350921f1a3789fea6e5149c7ed4a5","tid":255481,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"仲玩FB,唔死都冇用"},{"pid":"b9e1bf4624112ded087f9bb1e536e95ff6bd62c3","tid":255481,"uid":59163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:04:19.00